<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.6">
<l>kaiyum kālum nimirttuk kaṭāranīr</l>
<l>paiya vāṭṭip pacuñciṟu mañcaḷā</l>
<l>laiya nāvaḻit tāḷukkaṅ kāntiṭa</l>
<l>vaiya mēḻuṅkaṇ ṭāḷpiḷḷai vāyuḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When unfolding [his] arms and legs, gently bathing [him]</l>
<l>in the water of a cauldron, and opening [his] small mouth</l>
<l>to smear [his] tongue with a little [piece] of fresh tumeric</l>
<l>she saw the seven worlds in the mouth of the child.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
